---
import SocialIcons from './SocialIcons.astro';
---
<section class="pt-32 pb-16 text-center">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3">
      Camellia (Xinyue) Rui
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary mb-6">
      PhD Candidate in Biostatistics · University of Southern California
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto">
      I'm a research engineer building and evaluating AI agents for drug target discovery — grounded in human genetics and a statistical-genetics background.
      My dissertation focuses on probabilistically prioritizing causal variants underlying complex diseases.
      Currently AI Resident at <a href="https://xaira.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover">Xaira Therapeutics</a>.
      Previously ML intern at <a href="https://www.gene.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover">Genentech</a>.
      Advised by <a href="https://www.mancusolab.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover">Prof. Nick Mancuso</a> and <a href="https://gazal-lab.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover">Prof. Steven Gazal</a>.
      Final-year PhD candidate in Biostatistics at USC.
    </p>
    <SocialIcons />
  </div>
</section>
